    <h1>Dofollow</h1>
    <p class="description">The default state of any hyperlink. A dofollow link passes <strong>PageRank and ranking signals</strong> to the target page &mdash; and is defined by the <em>absence</em> of nofollow, sponsored, or ugc attributes, not by any positive marker.</p>
